Achievements.Name: Air Raid
Achievements.Description: Score 35+ points in a game running an Air Raid offense (excludes co-op).

Achievements.Name: Mix It Up
Achievements.Description: Rush for 100+ yards in a game with an Air Raid offense (excludes co-op).

Achievements.Name: Multiple Offense
Achievements.Description: Call at least one play from 10 different formation sets using a Multiple offense (excludes co-op).

Achievements.Name: One Back
Achievements.Description: Run a One Back offense and gain 200 yards rushing in a game (excludes co-op).

Achievements.Name: Options
Achievements.Description: Score 35+ points in a game running an Option offense (excludes co-op).

Achievements.Name: Throw 'Em a Curveball
Achievements.Description: Throw for 300 yards in one game using an Option offense (excludes co-op).

Achievements.Name: Pistol
Achievements.Description: Gain 100 yards rushing with a QB and a HB while running Pistol offense in a game (excludes co-op).

Achievements.Name: West Coast/Pro Style
Achievements.Description: Using a West Coast/Pro Style offense, complete passes to 8 different receivers (excludes co-op).

Achievements.Name: Run and Shoot
Achievements.Description: Gain 300 yards passing in a game throwing to at least 5 receivers using the Run and Shoot(no co-op).

Achievements.Name: Aggressive Spread No Huddle
Achievements.Description: Score a touchdown running only no huddle for an entire drive with a Spread offense (excludes co-op).

Achievements.Name: Spread No Huddle
Achievements.Description: With a Spread offense, score 2 TD's from audibled plays while running no huddle (excludes co-op).

Achievements.Name: There He Goes...
Achievements.Description: Break a run for 50 or more yards in a Play Now, Dynasty, or Road to Glory game (excludes co-op).

Achievements.Name: Take a Stab Downfield
Achievements.Description: Complete a pass for 50 or more yards in a Play Now, Dynasty, or Road to Glory game (excludes co-op).

Achievements.Name: Formation Sub Success
Achievements.Description: Score a touchdown with a player subbed in using Formation Subs (excludes co-op).

Achievements.Name: 1st Option For 6
Achievements.Description: Score a touchdown handing off to the fullback on a triple option play (excludes co-op).

Achievements.Name: Speed Reader
Achievements.Description: Score a touchdown on a QB Choice run play (excludes co-op).

Achievements.Name: Draw Me a Touchdown
Achievements.Description: Score a touchdown running a draw play on 3rd and 6+ yards (excludes co-op).

Achievements.Name: Hero
Achievements.Description: Score a touchdown as time expires to win the game (excludes co-op).

Achievements.Name: Balanced Attack
Achievements.Description: Gain 200 rushing yards and 200 passing yards in the same game (excludes co-op and Road to Glory).

Achievements.Name: The D Is For...
Achievements.Description: Hold the opposition to under 100 total yards in a Play Now or Dynasty Mode game (excludes co-op).

Achievements.Name: Red Zone Perfection
Achievements.Description: Complete a Play Now or Dynasty Mode game with a Red Zone Efficiency rating of 100% (excludes co-op).

Achievements.Name: Red Zone Shutout
Achievements.Description: Complete a Play Now or Dynasty Mode game without allowing a TD from the Red Zone (excludes co-op).

Achievements.Name: Lock It Up
Achievements.Description: With Player Lock on, return an interception for a TD (excludes co-op).

Achievements.Name: In Your Crosshairs
Achievements.Description: Spotlight a receiver and get an interception on him in a Play Now or Dynasty game (excludes co-op).

Achievements.Name: Veteran
Achievements.Description: Win a game by 35+ points on Heisman difficulty (excludes co-op).

Achievements.Name: Best Class Ever
Achievements.Description: Have the #1 ranked recruiting class in a season in single team Dynasty Mode.

Achievements.Name: Point Some Fingers
Achievements.Description: In a single phone call, take 250 points away from one school by downplaying pitches.

Achievements.Name: One Hit Wonder
Achievements.Description: Get an instant commit from a prospect by offering a scholarship on a one topic call.

Achievements.Name: Switcheroo
Achievements.Description: Secure a commitment from a prospect that was a soft commit elsewhere.

Achievements.Name: Don't Call It a Comeback
Achievements.Description: Convince a player with an overall rating of 95 or higher to stay.

Achievements.Name: Program Changer
Achievements.Description: Sign a 5-star QB or HB with a 2-star prestige school in a single team Dynasty (no ATH).

Achievements.Name: Setup Shop In the Big 3
Achievements.Description: In a single team Dynasty, develop new pipelines in Texas, California, and Florida.

Achievements.Name: Burn That Shirt
Achievements.Description: Remove the redshirt from a player in a game, and earn player of the game status with that player.

Achievements.Name: Crash the Party
Achievements.Description: In a single team Dynasty, earn an invite to a BCS game with a team from a non-BCS conference.

Achievements.Name: Picking Up Yards
Achievements.Description: In a solo Dynasty or Road to Glory season, have a player with an avg 6+ yds per carry (min 100 att).

Achievements.Name: Mr. Efficiency
Achievements.Description: In a solo Dynasty or Road to Glory season, have a QB with a completion % of 65+ (min. 100 attempts).

Achievements.Name: 20/20 Club
Achievements.Description: In a solo Dynasty or Road to Glory season, get 20+ passing and 20+ rushing TD's with one player.

Achievements.Name: What a Weekend
Achievements.Description: Invite 5 or more recruits to a game and get all A- or better visit grades in a single user Dynasty.

Achievements.Name: Survivor
Achievements.Description: Be the last remaining undefeated team in a single team Dynasty season.

Achievements.Name: Simply Perfect
Achievements.Description: Play an entire season in a single team Dynasty and remain undefeated.

Achievements.Name: Perfect From the Start
Achievements.Description: In a single team Dynasty, maintain a #1 ranking for the entire season.

Achievements.Name: Untouchable
Achievements.Description: In a single team Dynasty, win all games in a season by 21+.  (Must play the BCS title game)

Achievements.Name: Treasure Hunter
Achievements.Description: Win all bowl trophies (including National Championship) in Dynasty or Road to Glory modes.

Achievements.Name: High School Champ
Achievements.Description: Play and win the High School Championship Game in any state.

Achievements.Name: Blue Chip
Achievements.Description: Become a 5-star prospect in Road to Glory Mode.

Achievements.Name: Earned Your PT
Achievements.Description: Become a starter in Road to Glory Mode.

Achievements.Name: Strike the Pose
Achievements.Description: Win the Heisman Memorial Trophy® in single team Dynasty Mode or Road to Glory Mode.

Achievements.Name: Campus Legend
Achievements.Description: In Road to Glory Mode, earn a spot on your team's All-Time leaderboard.

Achievements.Name: Head and Shoulders Above
Achievements.Description: In Road to Glory Mode, earn a spot on your conference's All-Time leaderboard.

Achievements.Name: Greatness
Achievements.Description: In Road to Glory Mode, earn a spot on the NCAA All-Time leaderboard.
